OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778119410
OL,3,CKeir Starmer faces judgment day as
OL,4,Cmillions head to polling stations
OL,6,FIn Scotland, all 129 seats are up for
OL,7,Felection at Holyrood while voters in
OL,8,FWales will choose 96 members of the
OL,9,FSenedd.
OL,11,FAhead of polling day, Sir Keir said:
OL,12,F"In tough times, you need politicians
OL,13,Fwho will always stand up for you and
OL,14,Fyour family. Time and again Nigel
OL,15,FFarage and Zack Polanski have shown
OL,16,Fthey are not fit to meet this moment
OL,17,Fof great global instability.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778119410
OL,3,CKeir Starmer faces judgment day as
OL,4,Cmillions head to polling stations
OL,6,F"Today I pledge firmly to you:
OL,7,Fwhatever the pressure, Labour will
OL,8,Falways back you and your family and we
OL,9,Fwill never waver from doing what is in
OL,10,FBritain's national interest.
OL,12,F"Today, choose unity over division.
OL,13,FVote Labour."
OL,15,FConservative leader Kemi Badenoch said
OL,16,Fher party is the only one "with the
OL,17,Fplan, the team and the backbone to
OL,18,Fdeliver a stronger economy and
OL,19,Fstronger country".
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUuD@MO]xD@[OU{D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
