OL,3,CKeir Starmer faces judgment day as
OL,4,Cmillions head to polling stations
OL,6,FHe added: "We have less than 24 hours
OL,7,Fto stop Reform and defend the country
OL,8,Fwe love from Nigel Farage's Trump-
OL,9,Fstyle politics.
OL,11,F"We've now seen what Reform looks like
OL,12,Fin power ` banning journalists,
OL,13,Fscrapping renewables, closing care
OL,14,Fhomes and raising council tax despite
OL,15,Ftheir promises. Our communities can't
OL,16,Fafford that chaos.
OL,26,@nD@KOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
