OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778119410
OL,3,CKeir Starmer faces judgment day as
OL,4,Cmillions head to polling stations
OL,6,F"Reform made history and won the local
OL,7,Felections last year. If you really
OL,8,Fwant change, go out and vote for it
OL,9,Fagain today."
OL,11,FGreen Party leader Zack Polanski said
OL,12,Fhe will lead his party to "record-
OL,13,Fbreaking local elections" and "win
OL,14,Fmore councillors than ever before".
OL,16,FHe added: "In Wales, we are confident
OL,17,F` but not complacent ` of a historic
OL,18,Fbreakthrough in the Senedd elections.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@MO]tD@[OUuD@YO]uD@_OUvD@bO]xD@
OL,26,AKOU
