OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778119410
OL,3,CKeir Starmer faces judgment day as
OL,4,Cmillions head to polling stations
OL,6,F"Greens are the only party taking the
OL,7,Fcost-of-living crisis seriously, with
OL,8,Freal plans to cut bills, reduce rents
OL,9,Fand provide genuinely affordable
OL,10,Fhomes. It's a message that has been
OL,11,Freceived positively on the doorstep,
OL,12,Fbut now we have to to turn that warm
OL,13,Fsentiment into hard-won votes at the
OL,14,Fballot box."
OL,16,FPolling day will be the biggest test
OL,17,Ffor the Prime Minister since the
OL,18,Fgeneral election in 2024, with MPs
OL,19,Freportedly moving to oust him in the
OL,20,Fwake of the results.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@LO]
