OL,3,CKeir Starmer faces judgment day as
OL,4,Cmillions head to polling stations
OL,6,FBackbenchers from the 2024 intake are
OL,7,Fplotting to write a missive blaming
OL,8,Fthe Prime Minister for expected losses
OL,9,Fat the polls and asking him to set a
OL,10,Fdate for his departure, according to
OL,11,Fthe Times newspaper.
OL,13,FThe move would echo the drafting of a
OL,14,Fround-robin letter by normally loyal
OL,15,FLabour MPs calling for Sir Tony Blair
OL,16,Fto step down in September 2006.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
