OL,3,CKeir Starmer faces judgment day as
OL,4,Cmillions head to polling stations
OL,6,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,7,Fstood by Sir Keir, describing him as a
OL,8,F"level-headed" leader in an interview
OL,9,Fwith LBC, adding "the last thing that
OL,10,Fpeople will want is the Labour Party
OL,11,Fturning in on ourselves".
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@NO]qD@ROUsD@XO]
